# Workflow 11 — AI Invoice + Follow Up System
## Complete Master Notes

---

## What This Workflow Does

Someone fills a Google Form with client details.
Invoice email goes out automatically within 1 minute.
Sheet gets updated — Invoice Sent = Yes.
Workflow waits 3 days.
Checks if client paid.
Paid = stops. Unpaid = friendly reminder sent automatically.
Everything tracked in Google Sheets.

---

## Tools Used

```
Google Form   → Collect client and invoice details
Google Sheets → Track invoice and payment status
n8n           → Run the automation
OpenAI        → Write invoice and follow up emails
Gmail         → Send emails to clients
```

---

## Full Flow

```
Client fills Google Form
          ↓
01 - Watch New Invoice
     Checks Sheet every 1 minute
          ↓
02 - Extract Invoice Data
     Cleans and sets default values
          ↓
03 - AI Write Invoice Email
     GPT-4o-mini writes professional email
          ↓
04 - Parse AI Response
     Extracts subject + body
     Combines all data in one place
          ↓
05 - Send Invoice Email
     Sends to client via Gmail
          ↓
06 - Mark Invoice Sent
     Sheet update — Invoice Sent = Yes
          ↓
07 - Wait 3 Days
     Workflow pauses
          ↓
08 - Check Payment Status
     Reads fresh data from Sheet
          ↓
09 - IF Paid or Not
     Paid = stop | Unpaid = follow up
          ↓
10 - Send Follow Up Email
     Friendly reminder to client
```

