# Episode 2 — Node 01 — Watch New Invoice

## Node Info
```
Node Type : Google Sheets Trigger
Node Name : 01 - Watch New Invoice
Job       : Checks Sheet every 1 minute
            New row = workflow fires
```

## Config
```
Credential : Google account
Trigger On : Row Added
Spreadsheet: Invoice Request Form (Responses)
Sheet      : Form Responses 1
Poll Times : Every 1 Minute
```

## Why I Built It This Way
This is the starting gun of the workflow.
Every time a client submits the form, this catches it.
Polling every 1 minute means no lead waits more than 60 seconds.
Fetch Test Event pulls the latest form response for testing.
No need to submit a real form every time I test.

## Critical Mistake I Avoided
Never write to this Sheet from n8n.
Google Form writes here automatically.
n8n writing here too = double row problem.
This Sheet is read only for n8n.

