# Episode 9 — Node 08 — Check Payment Status

## Node Info
```
Node Type : Google Sheets — Get Row
Node Name : 08 - Check Payment Status
Job       : Reads fresh payment status from Sheet
            after the 3 day wait
```

## Config
```
Spreadsheet       : Invoice Request Form (Responses)
Sheet             : Form Responses 1
Column to match on: Client Email
Value             : {{ $('04 - Parse AI Response').item.json.client_email }}
```

## Why I Built It This Way
Owner may have manually marked the invoice as Paid during the 3 day wait.
I need fresh data — not the data from before the wait.
Getting the row fresh from Sheet gives me the current real status.
If I used cached data I might send a follow up to someone who already paid.
That looks unprofessional and damages the client relationship.

