# Episode 10 — Node 09 — IF Paid or Not

## Node Info
```
Node Type : IF Node
Node Name : 09 - IF Paid or Not
Job       : Checks Status — stops if Paid
            sends follow up if Unpaid
```

## Config
```
Value 1      : {{ $json.Status }}
Operation    : Equal
Value 2      : Paid
Convert types: ON
```

## Output
```
True Branch  → Paid → Workflow ends
False Branch → Unpaid → Follow up email sent
```

## Why I Built It This Way
Sending a reminder to someone who already paid is embarrassing.
This check prevents that completely.
True branch has no node connected — workflow just stops.
Convert types ON prevents string vs text comparison failures.

