# All Lessons Learned

```
Lesson 1 — Double Row Problem
Form Response Sheet = read only for n8n.
Google Form writes there automatically.
n8n writing there too = every entry appears twice.

Lesson 2 — Data Loss After Send Nodes
After Gmail Send node, $json loses all workflow data.
Always reference the last data node by name:
$('04 - Parse AI Response').item.json.client_email ✅
$json.client_email ❌

Lesson 3 — Data Loss After Wait Node
Same rule applies after Wait node.
$json does not survive a Wait.
Always use node name reference.

Lesson 4 — Get Fresh Data After Wait
After waiting 3 days, always read fresh data from Sheet.
Owner may have manually updated Status during the wait.
Cached data gives wrong results.

Lesson 5 — Convert Types in IF Node
Always ON. Without it, text comparisons fail silently.
Workflow runs but goes to the wrong branch.

Lesson 6 — OpenAI Response Path
output[0].content[0].text ✅
message.content ❌

Lesson 7 — Wait Node Testing
Use 1 Minute for testing.
Use 3 Days for production.
Never deploy with 1 Minute — clients get spammed.
```

