# Exam Results

```
Q1: Why is $json.client_email undefined after Wait node?
A:  Because workflow pauses — $json does not persist.
    Fix: $('04 - Parse AI Response').item.json.client_email ✅

Q2: Why must Convert types be ON in IF node?
A:  Without it, string values cannot be compared reliably.
    Comparison fails silently — wrong branch taken.

Q3: Why never write to Form Response Sheet from n8n?
A:  Google Form already writes there.
    n8n writing too = same data appears twice = double row problem.
```

